WEBVTT

00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:01.260
By the way,

00:00:01.260 --> 00:00:02.340
that girl is the one

00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:04.200
he's gonna marry, right?

00:00:07.180 --> 00:00:07.760
Hey.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.460
Why did he need a doctor?

00:00:09.940 --> 00:00:11.060
Don't tell me...

00:00:11.420 --> 00:00:12.200
he's got ED?

00:00:15.320 --> 00:00:16.920
Just a routine urology check.

00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:18.600
Don't pry into

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:19.520
others' privacy.

00:00:25.540 --> 00:00:26.390
I'm busy today.

00:00:26.440 --> 00:00:27.340
Eat by yourself.

00:00:27.460 --> 00:00:28.260
Hey! Wait...

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:38.880
Why are you here?

00:00:41.960 --> 00:00:42.600
Afternoon.

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:44.200
I'm Charles's friend.

00:00:48.040 --> 00:00:48.840
Afternoon.

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.000
When did you

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:51.580
have such a hot friend?

00:00:53.340 --> 00:00:54.680
Uh... we just met.

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:56.200
We're not that close.

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.100
There are no tables left.

00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:03.860
Can I join you?

00:01:04.480 --> 00:01:05.740
Yeah, sure.

00:01:06.100 --> 00:01:06.940
Please, sit.

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:27.560
Charles, are you okay?

00:01:29.140 --> 00:01:29.920
I'm fine...

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:31.300
Just having a cramp.

00:01:32.520 --> 00:01:33.060
Well...

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:34.960
You gotta be careful.

00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:37.400
Don't go cramping your third leg.

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:47.260
It's not hot in here,

00:01:47.260 --> 00:01:49.000
but why are you sweating so much?

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.080
I'm ok...

00:01:57.280 --> 00:01:59.000
I'm sorry, I'll clean it up.

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:00.720
It's okay. Let me help.

